stories.title: Australia romp home after Clarke hundred
stories.subTitle: Australia v Pakistan, VB Series, Sydney
stories.summary: Pakistan's troubled times in Australia continued as they put in a mediocre performance against some high-quality Australian bowling on a lively pitch at the Sydney Cricket Ground, and slumped to a nine-wicket loss
